atile way of cooking, you can even steam desserts such as <i>Pineapple Parcels<\/i>!","To blanch spinach: weigh into simmering basket, place over a large bowl or over sink and pour boiling water over then set aside. This will keep the colour vibrant as well as prevent water leaking from the spinach into the parcel when it cooks.","Works well served with rice.","Use your favourite type of tofu with this recipe.."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","30m","4 portions"]}